'''帕拉納克市巴士事故'''（{{lang-en|Parañaque bus accident}}）是一起發生於2013年12月16日的交通事故。一台巴士行駛於[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[馬尼拉|馬尼拉]]附近的[[帕拉納克市|帕拉納克市]]的{{link-en|南呂宋高速公路|South Luzon Expressway}}（{{link-en|馬尼拉大都會天路|Metro Manila Skyway}}）時墜落高架橋下<ref>{{cite web|title=Philippines bus crash kills 21|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25396084|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2013-12-16|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111192134/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25396084|dead-url=no}}</ref>，造成至少22人死亡，20人受傷<ref>{{cite web|last=Mogato|first=Manuel|title=Commuter bus crashes off Philippine highway onto van, 22 dead: police|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/16/us-philippines-accident-idUSBRE9BF03D20131216|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|accessdate=2013-12-16|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924191754/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/12/16/us-philippines-accident-idUSBRE9BF03D20131216|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 事故 ==
事故發生於[[馬尼拉大都會|馬尼拉大都會]][[帕拉納克市|帕拉納克市]]早上5時15分左右（當地時區[[UTC+7|UTC+7]]）<ref>{{cite web|title=Bus falls off freeway, kills 15 in Philippines|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/12/15/world/asia/philippines-bus-crash/|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2013-12-16|archive-date=2020-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118111855/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/12/15/world/asia/philippines-bus-crash/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一台巴士從6公尺高的{{link-en|南呂宋高速公路|South Luzon Expressway}}墜下，最後掉落在橋下道路並波及一輛卡車<ref>{{cite web|last=Placido|first=Dharel|title=Don Mariano bus falls off Skyway; scores dead|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/metro-manila/12/15/13/least-15-dead-bus-falls-skyway|publisher=ABS-CBN News|accessdate=2013-12-16|archive-date=2014-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141227145134/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/nation/metro-manila/12/15/13/least-15-dead-bus-falls-skyway|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴士的20名乘客及貨車裡的兩位民眾身亡，巴士駕駛則倖免於難<ref>{{cite web|title=Philippines bus plunges off highway, killing 22|url=http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/philippines-bus-plunges-off-highway-killing-22/story-e6frg6so-1226784244245|publisher=AFP via The Australian|accessdate=2013-12-16|archive-date=2013-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216132042/http://www.theaustralian.com.au/news/world/philippines-bus-plunges-off-highway-killing-22/story-e6frg6so-1226784244245|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 調查 ==
事故巴士所屬的唐馬里亞諾交通（{{lang-en|Don Mariano Transit}}）因接受調查被迫中止營業30天。[[菲律賓運輸及通訊部|菲律賓運輸及通訊部]]則對陸上交通特許單位及監管委員會下達指示，停止多恩馬里亞諾交通所擁有的78台巴士繼續行駛。此外，事故駕駛必須接受[[藥檢|藥檢]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Driver of ill-fated Don Mariano bus to undergo drug test|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/340001/news/metromanila/driver-of-ill-fated-don-mariano-bus-to-undergo-drug-test|publisher=GMA News|accessdate=2013-12-16|archive-date=2013-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217032352/http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/340001/news/metromanila/driver-of-ill-fated-don-mariano-bus-to-undergo-drug-test|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

